  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Line <math alttext=\"r\"><mi>r</mi>\n</math> is defined by the equation <math alttext=\"4 x minus 9 y equals 3\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t<mn>4</mn>\n\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t<mo>-</mo>\n\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t<mn>9</mn>\n\t\t\t<mi>y</mi>\n\t\t</mrow>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mn>3</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>. Line <math alttext=\"s\"><mi>s</mi>\n</math> is parallel to line <math alttext=\"r\"><mi>r</mi>\n</math> in the <em>xy</em>-plane. What is the slope of line <math alttext=\"s\"><mi>s</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
